subject: Automobile Racing
organizations: National Assn of Stock Car Auto Racing
lead_paragraph: Jeff Gordon won the Subway Fresh Fit 500 on Saturday night, tying Dale Earnhardt for sixth place on the career victory list for Nascar’s premier series.
